name: Get To 88
description:
IN THE DISTANT FUTURE, Year 1989,  a radical car NEEDS TO GO FAST! Fast car eats garbage and goes fast! Will that car ever reach that city skyline?  GO FASTER! CAR will go so fast, that if it goes 88 miles per hour faster, it will literally go into time.

Now Available on personal computer!

Made in a short amount of time for an event with an indie game station to promote local games. The event was scifi/fantasy themed, sooooo, maybe you can figure out the inspiration for this if you think reaaal fast.
